Powers.DescShort: Auto: +Res(Placate, Confuse, Taunt, Cold, Lethal, Smash) +Def(Melee, Ranged, AoE)
Powers.DescLong: Lionesses are resistant to Placate and Confuse effects as well as cold, lethal and smashing damage.  They also have a minor amount of defense to Melee, Ranged and AoE attacks.
